description: Learn how to talk like Yoda. Ask Alexa to translate, and find out just how Yoda would have said it, in his Yodish way.  Try it with jokes, emails, song lyrics, whatever!  Initial development based on this fine essay on the rules of 'Yodish': Yodish Analysis!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Yoda Translator to translate "How are you, today?"
Translate "You must have patience, young one."
Yoda, say "Here's my number, call me maybe".
name: Yoda Translator
shortDescription: With the Yoda Translator, you can ask Alexa to translate a sentence from English to Yodish!
